text: Grading for the 2025 Invitational Round has concluded. Participant scores, individual medals/awards, best solution awards, and the USA and Anglophone Canada team assignments for the 2025 IOL can be accessed here. Thank you for participating in NACLO 2025!
Grading for the 2025 Open Round has concluded and your score is available in your student account. The list of students who have qualified for the Invitational Round has been released.
We have published the list of submitted booklets. If you are a student and don't see your booklet here, please contact your site host.
Thank you to all who participated in the first round of NACLO 2025! Scores will be posted by the end of February. The Invitational Round will take place on Thursday, March 13, 2025.
Registration for NACLO will close on Monday, January 20th at 10 p.m. EST. Site registration will close at the same time. Some sites may accept walk-ins.
Registration is now open for the Open Round of the competition on January 23, 2025. Register here!
Registration for NACLO 2025 has not yet opened. Registration will open soon, so keep an eye on this page for updates.
